cs.AR, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SY, cs.ET. 

The paper is about a hardware architecture for accelerating deep learning computations, specifically for convolutional neural networks. Therefore, cs.AR (Hardware Architecture) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely categories. Additionally, since the focus is on image processing, cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also a likely category. The paper also discusses the ability to reconfigure the hardware at runtime, which falls under cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.ET (Embedded Systems).
